citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:43AM on 01-
AUG-23.
The inspectors arrived at 10:43AM on 08/01/23 to conduct an inspection. The inspectors attempted to contact the
Registrant by the provided phone numbers on arrival and did speak with a family member. Registrant was not at the
facility to conduct inspection. An AWA compliance inspection could not be conducted because there was no other
authorized facility representative available to accompany the inspectors.
Unannounced inspections are used to evaluate compliance with the AWA Regulations and Standards. This is the First
attempted inspection of the Registrant.
Additional Inspectors:
Karla Wills, ANIMAL CARE INSPECTOREnd Section
